spell_list.description: When Divine Fate of Healing Triggers, it can clear the reuse on Repent. Additionally, Mark of Nobility will increase the target's chance to strikethrough and, if the target is not a fighter, reduce their hate generation.
spell_list.description_pvp: When Divine Fate of Healing Triggers, it can clear the reuse on Repent. Additionally, Mark of Nobility will increase the target's chance to strikethrough and, if the target is not a fighter, reduce their hate generation.

effect_list.description: Divine Fate of Healing has a 30% chance to clear the reuse on Repent. This effect can only trigger once every 5 seconds.
Mark of Nobility will increase the target's strikethrough by 8%. If the target is not a fighter, Mark of Nobility will also reduce their hate gain by 8%.
